---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Dati aperti sullo spazio aereo italiano"
  description="FlyItalyADSB raccoglie dati ADS-B e MLAT sull'Italia per ricerca meteorologica e aeronautica. No-profit, gestito da appassionati."
>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="relative" style="height:90vh;min-height:560px">

    <iframe
      src="https://mappa.flyitalyadsb.com"
      title="Mappa ADS-B live"
      class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full border-0"
      loading="lazy"
      sandbox="allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups"
    ></iframe>

    <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none"
         style="background:linear-gradient(to bottom, #070d1acc 0%, #070d1a22 30%, #070d1a22 60%, #070d1aff 100%)">
    </div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none"
         style="background:linear-gradient(to right, #070d1acc 0%, transparent 60%)">
    </div>

    <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center px-6 sm:px-12 lg:px-20 pt-14">
      <div class="max-w-xl">

        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-medium mb-5"
             style="background:#38bdf815;border:1px solid #38bdf830;color:#7dd3fc">
          <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-green-400 animate-pulse inline-block"></span>
          Live · aggiornato ogni 0.2s
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold leading-tight mb-4" style="color:#f0f9ff">
          Dati ADS-B aperti<br />
          <span style="color:#38bdf8">copertura globale</span><br />
          MLAT italiano
        </h1>

        <p class="text-slate-400 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8 max-w-md">
          Raccogliamo dati ADS-B e Mode-S da tutto il mondo,
          con MLAT attivo sull'Italia — inclusi militari. No-profit, non filtrati.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <a href="https://mappa.flyitalyadsb.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
             class="px-5 py-2.5 rounded-lg font-medium text-sm no-underline transition-all"
             style="background:#38bdf8;color:#070d1a"
             onmouseover="this.style.background='#7dd3fc'"
             onmouseout="this.style.background='#38bdf8'">
            Esplora la mappa →
          </a>
          <a href="/ricerca"
             class="px-5 py-2.5 rounded-lg font-medium text-sm no-underline transition-all text-slate-200 hover:text-white"
             style="background:#ffffff10;border:1px solid #ffffff18"
             onmouseover="this.style.background='#ffffff18'"
             onmouseout="this.style.background='#ffffff10'">
            Ricerca
          </a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="absolute bottom-8 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 flex flex-col items-center gap-1 text-slate-600 pointer-events-none">
      <span class="text-xs">scorri</span>
      <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" class="animate-bounce">
        <path d="M12 5v14m0 0l-7-7m7 7l7-7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
      </svg>
    </div>

  </section>

  <!-- 3 PILLARS -->
  <section class="py-20 px-6 sm:px-12 lg:px-20 max-w-7xl mx-auto">

    <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-10">Cosa raccogliamo</p>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">

      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border" style="background:#0f1929;border-color:#1e3048">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4"
             style="background:#38bdf815;border:1px solid #38bdf830">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#38bdf8" stroke-width="1.5">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/>
            <path d="M12 2v3m0 14v3M2 12h3m14 0h3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-100 mb-2">Copertura globale ADS-B</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
          Feed aggregato da ricevitori italiani, adsb.lol e theairtraffic.com. Copertura mondiale, densità elevata sopra l'Italia e il Mediterraneo.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-4 text-xs font-mono text-slate-600">aircraft.json · 0.2s</div>
      </div>

      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border" style="background:#0f1929;border-color:#1e3048">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4"
             style="background:#38bdf815;border:1px solid #38bdf830">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#38bdf8" stroke-width="1.5">
            <path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5zM2 17l10 5 10-5M2 12l10 5 10-5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-100 mb-2">Triangolazione MLAT</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
          Multilateration su aerei senza transponder ADS-B completo, inclusi militari. Unico servizio MLAT attivo in Italia.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-4 text-xs font-mono text-slate-600">mlat-server · porta 30100</div>
      </div>

      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border" style="background:#0f1929;border-color:#1e3048">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4"
             style="background:#38bdf815;border:1px solid #38bdf830">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#38bdf8" stroke-width="1.5">
            <path d="M3 3h18v18H3zM3 9h18M9 21V9" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-100 mb-2">Mode-S BDS50/BDS60</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
          True Air Speed, magnetic heading e Mach number via Mode-S Comm-B. Dati per la ricostruzione del vento troposferico.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-4 text-xs font-mono text-slate-600">Mode-S EHS · BDS50 · BDS60</div>
      </div>

    </div>

  </section>

  <!-- RICERCA IN EVIDENZA -->
  <section class="py-20 px-6 sm:px-12 lg:px-20 max-w-7xl mx-auto border-t" style="border-color:#1e3048">

    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-end justify-between gap-4 mb-10">
      <div>
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Ricerca in corso</p>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-100">Dall'airspace alla scienza</h2>
      </div>
      <a href="/ricerca" class="text-sm text-sky-400 hover:text-sky-300 no-underline">Tutti i progetti →</a>
    </div>

    <!-- Featured: weather-32 -->
    <a href="/ricerca/weather" class="block p-8 rounded-2xl border no-underline group transition-all hover:border-sky-400/30 mb-6"
       style="background:#0f1929;border-color:#1e3048">
      <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-8">
        <div class="flex-1">
          <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <span class="text-xs px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full font-medium" style="background:#38bdf815;color:#7dd3fc;border:1px solid #38bdf830">Meteorologia</span>
            <span class="text-xs px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full font-medium" style="background:#10b98115;color:#34d399;border:1px solid #10b98130">In corso</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-100 mb-3 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
            Misura del vento troposferico da aeromobili in volo
          </h3>
          <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4 max-w-2xl">
            Gli aerei commerciali in volo sono sensori meteorologici distribuiti ad alta quota.
            Estraendo le componenti di vento dai messaggi Mode-S (BDS50/BDS60) e confrontandole
            con le rianalisi ERA5 e i profili IASI, stiamo validando la qualità del dato aeronautico
            come sorgente meteorologica indipendente.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-6 text-sm">
            <div>
              <div class="text-xs text-slate-600 uppercase tracking-wider mb-1">Metodo</div>
              <div class="text-slate-300 font-mono text-xs">W = V<sub>ground</sub> − V<sub>air</sub></div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-xs text-slate-600 uppercase tracking-wider mb-1">Validazione</div>
              <div class="text-slate-300 text-xs">ERA5 · IASI (MetOp)</div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-xs text-slate-600 uppercase tracking-wider mb-1">RMSE tipico</div>
              <div class="text-slate-300 text-xs">6.5–7.4 m/s (u, v)</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Mini risultati -->
        <div class="shrink-0 w-full lg:w-64 p-5 rounded-xl" style="background:#111e30;border:1px solid #1e3048">
          <div class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Mode-S vs ERA5</div>
          <div class="space-y-3">
            {[
              { label: 'Bias u', value: '+0.21 m/s' },
              { label: 'Bias v', value: '+1.77 m/s' },
              { label: 'RMSE u', value: '7.38 m/s' },
              { label: 'RMSE v', value: '6.57 m/s' },
            ].map(row => (
              <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
                <span class="text-xs text-slate-500">{row.label}</span>
                <span class="text-xs font-mono" style="color:#7dd3fc">{row.value}</span>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
          <div class="mt-4 pt-3 border-t text-xs text-slate-600" style="border-color:#1e3048">23 giu 2025</div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </a>

  </section>

  <!-- COMMUNITY CTA -->
  <section class="py-20 px-6 sm:px-12 lg:px-20 max-w-7xl mx-auto border-t" style="border-color:#1e3048">

    <div class="rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-12 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-8 items-start sm:items-center justify-between"
         style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0f1929 0%,#111e30 100%);border:1px solid #1e3048">

      <div class="max-w-lg">
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-3" style="color:#38bdf8">Contribuisci</p>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-100 mb-3">Fai parte della rete</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          La qualità dei dati dipende dalla densità della rete. Con un Raspberry Pi e un'antenna RTL-SDR
          puoi contribuire a coprire la tua area. Tutto il necessario costa meno di €30.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 shrink-0">
        <a href="/community/feeder"
           class="px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-medium text-sm text-center no-underline transition-all"
           style="background:#38bdf8;color:#070d1a"
           onmouseover="this.style.background='#7dd3fc'"
           onmouseout="this.style.background='#38bdf8'">
          Diventa feeder →
        </a>
        <a href="/chi-siamo"
           class="px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-medium text-sm text-center no-underline transition-all text-slate-300 hover:text-white"
           style="background:#ffffff08;border:1px solid #ffffff14"
           onmouseover="this.style.background='#ffffff12'"
           onmouseout="this.style.background='#ffffff08'">
          Chi siamo
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>

  </section>

</Layout>
